  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2026-03-20",
    "date": "2026-03-23T13:50:28Z",
    "text": "This resolution recognizes the importance of fully funding the Department of Homeland Security (DHS).\n\nThe resolution also (1) cautions that Americans are at greater risk each day\u00a0DHS is subject to a lapse in appropriations, and (2) expresses gratitude to DHS employees for their commitment to protect the United States.\u00a0"
